const mvp = require('./mvp');


module.exports = [mvp];

const Recipe = `#graphql
    type Recipe {
        id: ID!
        steps: [String!]!
        date: String!
        userid: ID!
        title: String!
        link: [String!]
        cookingtime_min: Int!
        views: Int!
        votes: Int!
        imageurl: String
    }
`



module.exports = Recipe;

const Ingredient = `#graphql
    type Ingredient {
        name: String!
        calories: Float!
        total_fat: Float!
        sat_fat: Float!
        protein: Float!
        sodium: Float!
        potassium: Float!
        cholesterol: Float!
        carbohydrates: Float!
        fiber: Float!
        sugar: Float!
        category: String!
        imageurl: String
    }
`


module.exports = Ingredient;
